    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast a spell that has a duration of 1 minute or longer, you can spend 1 sorcery point to increase its duration.</p><ul><li>If the duration of the spell is 1 minute, it is extended to 10 minutes.</li><li>If the duration of the spell is 10 minutes, it is extended to 1 hour.</li><li>If the duration of the spell is 1 hour, it is extended to 8 hours.</li><li>If the duration of the spell is 8 hours or greater, it is extended to 24 hours.</li></ul><p>Extend spell cannot extend the duration of a spell to over 24 hours.</p>",
